- The user is free tonight, and want to see what's going in or near his
  home location. (Default case)

- The user has a free evening in a foreign city and want to see what's
  going on in or near his location. (Default case for LBS)

- The user plans a visit in a particular region and wants to learn about
  events in that region at or near a certain date.

- The user has learned of a new artist and wants to add it to his favorites.
    - The artist already exists in the DB.
    - The artist is new to the DB

- The user has learned of a new event
    - The artist already exists in the DB
    - The artist is new to the DB
